en_535253_0	Officer Cadets of the Sri Lanka Military Academy (SLMA) as part of their course training modules, made a visit to the Vijayabahu Infantry Regiment (VIR) Headquarters at Boyagane on Sunday (17) and received a comprehensive knowledge on the role and tasks of a Regimental Headquarter.
en_535253_1	Brigadier Srinatha Ariyasingha, Centre Commandant Regimental Centre VIR welcomed and facilitated the visit of those Officer Cadets on the instructions of Major General Ajith Kariyakarawana, Deputy Chief of Staff & Colonel of the Regiment VIR.
